<p>After getting ditched by everyone, Matt and I decided to forgo the planned ride and do Boxing Boulder instead.</p>
<p>Matt has kindly <a href="http://trail.motionbased.com/trail/activity/3993095">recorded and published</a> all our vital signs from the ride, using his snazzy GPS "watch".  As you can see, despite the nagging winds and momentum-busting stoplights, we hemmed in our favorite town rather swiftly.</p>